# ── API Base URL ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Development: leave blank (Vite proxy handles /api → localhost:5000)
# Production:  MUST be set to your deployed backend URL — login/auth WILL FAIL
#              if this is left blank in production!
#
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT FOR DEPLOYMENT:
#   In your Vercel project settings → Environment Variables, add:
#   VITE_API_URL = https://your-backend.onrender.com/api
#   (Replace with your actual Render backend URL — no trailing slash)
#
# Local development (leave blank):
VITE_API_URL=
